<Link id="l00120" /><CodeLine lineNumber="120"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// Emits a warning if two values disagree. The result value will be the</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00124" /><CodeLine lineNumber="124"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// Adds a requirement that another module flag be present and have a</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00125" /><CodeLine lineNumber="125"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// specified value after linking is performed. The value must be a metadata</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00126" /><CodeLine lineNumber="126"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// pair, where the first element of the pair is the ID of the module flag</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00127" /><CodeLine lineNumber="127"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// to be restricted, and the second element of the pair is the value the</Highlight></CodeLine>
